title: Memphis Mane Comedy Special 2019 W DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & Chico Bean | Ep. 204
itunes:title: Memphis Mane Comedy Special 2019 W DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & Chico Bean | Ep. 204
description:
The coldest podcast returns to Memphis to check errrbody in the building! DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean waste no time brining the laughs and interacting with the people of Memphis, Tennessee! The squad deliver a classic show, paying tribute to Memphis rap and they take a trip down memory lane - back to when you had to ask your momma to stay over your friends house. If your looking for the funny real podcast - this is it! Get tickets to see them in San Diego! bit.ly/85sandiego2019 FOLLOW THE CREW KARLOUS MILLER - https://www.facebook.com/karlousm/ DCYOUNGFLY - https://www.facebook.com/DcYoungFly1/ CHICO BEAN - https://www.facebook.com/OldSchoolFool/ BILLY SORRELLS - https://www.facebook.com/billysorrells/ FAT AND PAID - https://www.facebook.com/Fatandpaid/ DARREN BRAND - https://www.facebook.com/darrenbigbab...
